ops and sets it on the table that Herc is sitting at::: Hippolyte, I don't know if you know my friend here.  This is Hercules, Hercules this is the lovely Queen Hippolyte of Themiscrya. Now, &quot;he smiles.&quot;please excuse me, while I take care of this order.&quot;<br>
